very delicious.
非常美味。

87
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,840
It is.
是的。

88
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:54,840
And sometimes you have this with a side of jalapeno.
有时候你会配上一些墨西哥辣椒。

89
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,840
Okay.
好的。

90
